00:00:00.969 --> 00:00:09.550
Honorary degrees recognize individuals who
by their outstanding service to the University,

00:00:09.550 --> 00:00:18.990
the state, the country and humanity exemplify
the mission and purposes of Binghamton University.

00:00:18.990 --> 00:00:25.630
Their lives and their achievements stand as
inspiration to us all.

00:00:25.630 --> 00:00:35.020
I am pleased to announce that we will now
confer the honorary degree of doctor of letters

00:00:35.020 --> 00:00:37.730
on David Sedaris.

00:00:37.730 --> 00:00:45.700
Mr. Sedaris is a writer, playwright, radio
personality who is a native of this area.

00:00:45.700 --> 00:01:06.420
Provost Swain will you please bring David
Sedaris to the podium.

00:01:06.420 --> 00:01:10.150
Provost Swain will you please read the citation.

00:01:10.150 --> 00:01:18.110
David Sedaris, distinguished writer and humorist,
you write and speak about the human condition

00:01:18.110 --> 00:01:24.250
through triumph and tragedy while encouraging
your audience to laugh at lives absurdities.

00:01:24.250 --> 00:01:30.600
A native of Binghamton, New York, your essays
are published in prestigious magazines, your

00:01:30.600 --> 00:01:37.280
stories are broadcast on national radio programs
and your books are best sellers.

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:41.880
You have been recognized for the quality of
your work through the Thurber Prize for American

00:01:41.880 --> 00:01:42.880
humor.

00:01:42.880 --> 00:01:50.260
Time Magazineâ€™s Humorist of the Year and
two Grammy award nominations for best-spoken

00:01:50.260 --> 00:01:52.030
word album.

00:01:52.030 --> 00:01:57.450
For all of these accomplishments as well of
those to come The State University of New

00:01:57.450 --> 00:02:05.860
York is proud to present you with the honorary
degree of Doctor of Letters.

00:02:05.860 --> 00:02:21.280
By virtue of the authority vested in me by
the State Board of the University of New York,

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:30.370
the Trustees, I confer upon you the degree
Doctor of Letters honoris causa and invest

00:02:30.370 --> 00:02:38.690
you with all the rights and privileges pertaining
there unto in token thereof we hand you this

00:02:38.690 --> 00:03:12.850
diploma and vest you with the hood appropriate
to this degree.

00:03:12.850 --> 00:03:16.160
Thank you President DeFleur and thank you
so much Binghamton University.

